    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Class containing all particle information. The array of particle containers has <computeroutput>n_species</computeroutput> number of particles containers, that is each responsible for one species of particles. For each particle the particle position, velocity and weight are stored in a ArrayOfStructs manner. The charge and mass of the particle species are stored in a separate array. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
